text: "Alright" is a 1995 song by English band Supergrass. It was released along its A-side Time. It was taken from their debut studio album I Should Coco. It was used on the soundtrack to the 1995 movie Clueless. It went to number 2 in the United Kingdom and Scotland, number 98 in Australia, number 30 in France, number 6 in Iceland, number 8 in Ireland and the Netherlands. ==Track listings== ==References== Category:1995 songs Category:Supergrass songs
